The paper focuses on face recognition and spoofing detection, which are both related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves training a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN), which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.MM) and the paper discusses the importance of learning deep features, which is a topic in deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also addresses security concerns, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper involves image processing and analysis, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR).
